{"tid":2081243,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"失業既時候，屋企人點樣\"鼓勵\"你搵工？","createTime":"2020-06-27T05:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T08:44:47.000Z","uid":9965,"like":13,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"87959fbf37cf869b8131ec7e9c5fa0219c24ad3d","tid":2081243,"uid":9965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:28:12.000Z","msg":"以前試過屋企3個男人都失業，得老母有做清潔<br />\n老母成日叫我地乜工都搵住先，老豆就話寧願自殺都唔轉行，我地就低既唔肯做，高既搵唔到<br />\n老母見屌極都無用就開始無聲抗議<br />\n<br />\n成日執d 電線返來開皮開到成地都係膠<br />\n夜晚開飯見我地訓緊覺就唔叫醒我地，一係就唔擺我地個位要我地自己拎碗裝飯<br />\n整左d 餸唔好食，食唔晒就放入雪櫃，第餐拎返出來，死都唔倒，結果果碟餸食左成個星期<br />\n<br />\n後尾老豆都係轉左行做d 人工低但舒服既悠位，我地就搵左第行由低做起半工讀結埋婚生埋B <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老母都好開心終於守得雲開見月明，有寶貝孫仔抱"},{"pid":"ff535557be6848af690b29bbcc2fc0616f09ca64","tid":2081243,"uid":136860,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:31:23.000Z","msg":"一係踩你一係叫你勞工處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5212c08d3e872ebb6f94fb5b24644a510191e153","tid":2081243,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:36:14.000Z","msg":"老母仲關心過我做野個陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"183ba645305f0f04ca3624b79fe4fdd75564e2c3","tid":2081243,"uid":196964,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:36:19.000Z","msg":"繼續拎家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2370f6ced3580243605e109337798e869922eb00","tid":2081243,"uid":309192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:37:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你成日坐係度賀壽做咩姐</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"80dc69d4ad509cb34fda016127f4f738d766bd43","tid":2081243,"uid":82542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:38:04.000Z","msg